la théorie de l'information,

199
0:10:48.721,000 --> 0:10:49,000
la théorie des jeux,

200
0:10:50.051,000 --> 0:10:51,000
l'acquisition comprimée,

201
0:10:51.515,000 --> 0:10:52,000
l'apprentissage automatique,

202
0:10:53.085,000 --> 0:10:54,000
l'analyse de graphique,

203
0:10:54.692,000 --> 0:10:55,000
l'analyse harmonique.

204
0:10:56.418,000 --> 0:10:58,000
